title: Aussie model slates Justin Bieber's 'small d**k' despite partying on his luxury yacht
text:
Aussie model slates Justin Bieber's 'small d**k' despite partying on his luxury yacht Aussie model slates Justin Bieber's 'small d**k' despite partying on his luxury yacht WE'RE guessing Sharah Fitzgerald is not a Belieber.   topless model spent last week partying with Justin Bieber, on-board his luxury yacht, but she seemed to have to get a little something off of her chest. 
Sharah took an epic swipe at the 23-year-old's manhood in a lengthy Instagram tirade.

GETTY POP HEARTTHROB: Yes, your abs are still there Biebs “Bieber looks like [he] just left church [and] stuck some transfer tats on to compensate [for] his small d**k” Sharah Fitzgerald 
In the scathing post, the yummy mummy uploaded a photo of both Justin and Mark Wahlberg's Calvin Klein campaigns. 
Sharah declared she was Team Wahlberg and ripped into the No Sense crooner. 
"Bieber looks like [he] just left church [and] stuck some transfer tats on to compensate [for] his small d**k and glorious 12-year-old body!" she wrote. The hottest Australian Instagram babes Wednesday, 21st September 2016 The babes from down under are taking over! Take a look at the hottest Australian babes we have found. 1 / 21 
INSTAGRAM PARTY BOAT: Sharah had just been partying on Justin's luxury yacht 
Although the post was from 2015, something tells us you won't be welcome back on the yacht Sharah. 
The Canadian singer welcomed an army of stunning women on his party boat last week, including Sharah and her sister Kaysha Louise. 
Sharah seemed to lap up the attention, posting shortly after on the boat trip on her Facebook account how "humble" Justin was. 
INSTAGRAM THE GOODS: Bieber loves to show off his bod 
We're not sure if some of Justin's fans would agree with you. 
The star has been attracting a lot of attention – mainly for the wrong reasons.
